OL,3,CManchester United legends gather for
OL,4,Cfuneral of Denis Law
OL,6,FFootball greats have gathered in
OL,7,FManchester to bid farewell to United
OL,8,Flegend and Scotland international
OL,9,FDenis Law.
OL,11,FThe Aberdeen-born striker died on 17
OL,12,FJanuary 2025, aged 84, more than three
OL,13,Fyears after he was diagnosed with
OL,14,FAlzheimer's disease and vascular
OL,15,Fdementia.
