OL,3,CManchester United legends gather for
OL,4,Cfuneral of Denis Law
OL,6,FLaw, known at 'The King', won two
OL,7,Fleague titles with Manchester United
OL,8,Fand was a member of their European Cup-
OL,9,Fwinning side under Sir Matt Busby in
OL,10,F1968 when they became the first
OL,11,FEnglish club to lift the trophy.
OL,13,FFlags around Old Trafford flew at half-
OL,14,Fmast as his hearse and funeral
OL,15,Fprocession passed Manchester United's
OL,16,Fstadium at around 1pm on Tuesday, 11
OL,17,FFebruary.
