OL,3,CManchester United legends gather for
OL,4,Cfuneral of Denis Law
OL,6,FThe packed route of the procession
OL,7,Ftook Chester Road, Sir Matt Busby Way
OL,8,Fand the East Stand forecourt, before
OL,9,Fpausing at the Trinity Statue.
OL,11,FIt then made its way to Manchester
OL,12,FCathedral for the service where
OL,13,Ffootball legends young and old
OL,14,Fgathered for the "King of the
OL,15,FStretford End."
OL,17,FSir Kenny Dalglish and Sir Alex
OL,18,FFerguson were among the mourners as
OL,19,Fthe footballing legend was remembered
OL,20,Fin the heart of the city he left an
OL,21,Findelible mark on.
