OL,3,CManchester United legends gather for
OL,4,Cfuneral of Denis Law
OL,6,FCurrent United head coach Ruben Amorim
OL,7,Falso joined fans, dignitaries and
OL,8,Ffigures from the footballing world for
OL,9,Fthe service.
OL,11,FBruno Fernandes, Harry Maguire, Tom
OL,12,FHeaton and Maya Le Tissier represented
OL,13,Fthe current teams, with chief
OL,14,Fexecutive Omar Berrada, Darren
OL,15,FFletcher and women's team boss Marc
OL,16,FSkinner also in attendance.
OL,18,FBrian Kidd, Alex Stepney and Willie
OL,19,FMorgan were among Law's former United
OL,20,Fteam-mates at the funeral, as was
OL,21,Fformer City team-mate Mike Summerbee.
