OL,6,FBryan Robson, Gary Neville, Paul
OL,7,FScholes, Pete Schmeichel and Ruud van
OL,8,FNistelrooy were others at the service.
OL,10,FThe wake will be held at Old Trafford.
OL,12,FLaw's family announced the news of his
OL,13,Fpassing in a statement which read: "It
OL,14,Fis with a heavy heart that we tell you
OL,15,Four father Denis Law has sadly passed
OL,16,Faway. He fought a tough battle but
OL,17,Ffinally he is now at peace.
