OL,3,CManchester United legends gather for
OL,4,Cfuneral of Denis Law
OL,6,F"We would like to thank everyone who
OL,7,Fcontributed to his wellbeing and care,
OL,8,Fpast and much more recently. We know
OL,9,Fhow much people supported and loved
OL,10,Fhim and that love was always
OL,11,Fappreciated and made the difference.
OL,12,FThank you."
OL,14,FLaw ` who scored 237 goals in 404
OL,15,Fappearances for United ` is the only
OL,16,Fplayer to have two statues dedicated
OL,17,Fto him at Old Trafford, one on the
OL,18,FStretford End concourse and the other
OL,19,Fas part of the 'United Trinity'
OL,20,Foutside the stadium alongside fellow
OL,21,Fgreats George Best and Bobby Charlton.
